## פרומפט מאסטר — להדביק בתחילת כל פרומפט

```
Photorealistic large-format vinyl sticker design for a storefront glass window.
Solid dark charcoal gray background (#2B2B2B).
Mix of: high-resolution photorealistic food product cutouts with soft drop shadows,
and simple hand-drawn outline illustrations of food items in cyan, yellow and green.
No text. No logos. No people.
Scattered abundance layout. Premium supermarket aesthetic.
Ultra high resolution, suitable for large format print.
Generate as a standalone image for a single panel.
```

